---
title: Smart Miso-Cranberry Pork Tenderloin with Fresh Clementine-Cashew Salad
description: It takes two to tango, and this miso-clementine flavour combo is ready for the dinnertime dance floor. Both umami-rich and fruity, the pork tenderloin is seared before being topped with miso-cranberry glaze.
